commentTextItems.html: there it is the winning runs come from the bat of Misbah-ul-Haq which is quite fitting seeing it is his birthday today. Jones strays to far onto leg stump and as Ireland had brought all the fielders up close there was no fielder on the leg boundary.
Younis is given more room outside the off stump and the ball is hit just wide of the fielder at mid-on
pitches on middle stump and swings away slightly and is well defended by Younis
just outside off stump and left alone alot easier this time by Misbah

headshotImage.caption: Nigel Jones player page headshot cutout, 2021
headshotImage.longCaption: Nigel Jones player page headshot cutout, 2021

commentTextItems.html: great shout for Ireland. Almost the same delivery that got Shaqif almost got Misbah too. The irish players cannot believe they havent given that out
on middle stump and hit to the fielder at point

dismissalText.commentary: Asad Shafiq c Wilson b Cusack 4 (12b 1x4 0x6 15m) SR: 33.33

commentTextItems.html: shorter this time from Cusack and clips the outside edge and goes through to Wilson. Maybe the comebacks on?
strayed down leg stump and clipped round the corner
a good length delivery driven through mid-wicket for four. It might not be long now
tighter line from Jones this time and it goes through to the keeper

commentTextItems.html: wider outside off stump and it gets crashed through point for four
good length again from Jones. Shaqif can only hit it back to him
shorter this time and back to the bowler
played straight back to the bowler from a good length ball
too far outside off stump
outside off stump and through to the keeper
